'''藍圍裙控股公司'''（{{lang-en|Blue Apron Holdings, Inc.}}）通稱'''藍圍裙'''（{{lang|en|Blue Apron}}）是一家美國[[快煮餐|快煮餐]]公司，總部位於[[紐約市|紐約市]]，僅營運於美國本土，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Blue Apron's Got Big Plans For Dinner -- But So Do Its Hungry Rivals|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/alexkonrad/2015/10/14/inside-blue-apron-and-the-meal-kit-rush/|date=2015-10-14|accessdate=2020-08-22|last=Konrad|first=Alex|work=[[富比士|Forbes]]|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727003420/https://www.forbes.com/sites/alexkonrad/2015/10/14/inside-blue-apron-and-the-meal-kit-rush/|dead-url=no}}</ref>提供顧客每周寄送餐盒的服務，餐盒內附有建議[[食譜|食譜]]和食材，使顧客可自行在家[[烹調|烹調]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=圈粉顧客，售後服務的6個策略|url=https://www.cw.com.tw/article/5097601|date=2019-11-07|author=洪培鈞|accessdate=2020-08-24|work=天下雜誌|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824085645/https://www.cw.com.tw/article/5097601|dead-url=no}}</ref>

截至2016年9月，該公司已出貨800萬份餐盒<ref>{{Cite web|title=Meal kits put to the test|url=https://www.thetimesherald.com/story/life/2016/09/01/meal-kits-put-test/89743878/|date=2016-09-02|accessdate=2020-08-22|last=Sherwood|first=Alison|work={{tsl|en|The Times Herald|時代先驅報|Times Herald}}|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824072636/https://www.thetimesherald.com/story/life/2016/09/01/meal-kits-put-test/89743878/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在2017年6月完成[[首次公開募股|首次公開募股]]後在[[紐約證券交易所|紐約證券交易所]]上市，成為美國首家[[股票上市|公開上市]]的快煮餐公司。<ref name="Lauren Hirsch">{{Cite news|title=Meal-kit maker Blue Apron goes public, demand underwhelms as Amazon looms|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-blueapron-ipo-idUSKBN19J1C5|author1=Lauren Hirsch|author2=Angela Moon|author3=Aparajita Saxena|editor1=Meredith Mazzilli|editor2=Richard Chang|newspaper=Reuters|date=2017-06-29|accessdate=2020-08-22|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727002633/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-blueapron-ipo-idUSKBN19J1C5|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
[[File:Blue_Apron_meal_kit_box.jpg|thumb]]
馬特·薩爾茲伯格（Matt Salzberg）、伊利亞·帕帕斯（Ilia Papas）和馬修·瓦迪亞克（Matthew Wadiak）於2012年8月開始向顧客提供裝有食材和建議食譜的餐盒，三人在[[長島市|長島市]]的一間商業廚房內包裝和運送首批收到的30個訂單。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Konrad|first1=Alex|title=Blue Apron's Got Big Plans For Dinner -- But So Do Its Hungry Rivals|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/alexkonrad/2015/10/14/inside-blue-apron-and-the-meal-kit-rush/#7b53675c6461|accessdate=2017-05-10|work=Forbes|date=2015-10-14|language=en|archive-date=2017-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170424135113/https://www.forbes.com/sites/alexkonrad/2015/10/14/inside-blue-apron-and-the-meal-kit-rush/#7b53675c6461|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年5月，藍圍裙宣布在[[加州|加州]][[里奇蒙_(加利福尼亞州)|里奇蒙]]建立[[履行中心|履行中心]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Blue Apron Brings 400 Jobs to Bay Area|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/blue-apron-brings-400-jobs-to-bay-area-260958001.html|accessdate=2017-05-10|publisher=PRNewswire|work=Blue Apron|date=2014-05-28|language=en|archive-date=2017-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171202052836/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/blue-apron-brings-400-jobs-to-bay-area-260958001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在同年11月推出烹飪工具商店「Blue Apron Market」，出售刀具、廚具、烘焙工具和[[烹飪書|烹飪書]]等廚房用具。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://techcrunch.com/2014/11/12/blue-apron-blows-past-1-million-meals-sold-each-month-looks-to-ecommerce/|title=Blue Apron Blows Past 1 Million Meals Sold Each Month, Looks To eCommerce|author=Jordan Crook|date=2014-11-12|website=techcrunch|accessdate=2017-07-05|language=en|archive-date=2017-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170706220206/https://techcrunch.com/2014/11/12/blue-apron-blows-past-1-million-meals-sold-each-month-looks-to-ecommerce/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年12月，藍圍裙於[[紐澤西州|紐澤西州]]的[[澤西市|澤西市]]開設另一座履行中心。<ref>{{cite news|title=Blue Apron Shipping Over One Million Meals per Month|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/blue-apron-shipping-over-one-million-meals-per-month-282395181.html|publisher=PRNewswire|date=2014-11-12|accessdate=2020-08-22|work=Blue Apron|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729131353/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/blue-apron-shipping-over-one-million-meals-per-month-282395181.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年6月，在[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]][[阿靈頓_(德克薩斯州)|阿靈頓]]開設第三座履行中心後，藍圍裙開始向美國內陸地區發展業務。<ref>{{cite news|title=Blue Apron to Open Arlington Fulfillment Center|url=http://www.arlington-tx.gov/news/2015/05/18/blue-apron-to-open-arlington-fulfillment-center/|accessdate=2017-05-10|publisher=Arlington City|date=2015-05-18|language=en|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211111330/http://www.arlington-tx.gov/news/2015/05/18/blue-apron-to-open-arlington-fulfillment-center/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年9月，藍圍裙推出[[葡萄酒|葡萄酒]]配送服務「Blue Apron Wine」，每月向顧客配送6瓶500毫升的葡萄酒<ref>{{Cite web|title=Can booze lure me back to a meal-delivery service?|url=https://www.theverge.com/2015/9/26/9401513/blue-apron-wine-delivery-on-demand-food-review|accessdate=2020-08-23|date=2015-09-26|last=Goode|first=Lauren|work=The Verge|language=en|archive-date=2017-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171204222824/https://www.theverge.com/2015/9/26/9401513/blue-apron-wine-delivery-on-demand-food-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由葡萄園專為該公司釀造，並在購買後經由第三方運送。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Meal delivery start-up Blue Apron to sell wine, sees growth opportunity|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-blueapron-wine-idUSKCN0RL19I20150921|author=Anjali Athavaley|newspaper=Reuters|date=2015-09-21|accessdate=2020-08-23|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727010201/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-blueapron-wine-idUSKCN0RL19I20150921|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年10月，網路媒體[[BuzzFeed|BuzzFeed]]報導指出藍圍裙以往在[[里奇蒙_(加利福尼亞州)|里奇蒙]]履行中心的食品衛生安全問題，而藍圍裙則將其歸咎於早期擴大業務規模的營運問題。<ref>{{cite web|last1=O'Donovan|first1=Caroline|title=The Not-So-Wholesome Reality Behind The Making of Your Meal Kit|url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/carolineodonovan/the-not-so-wholesome-reality-behind-the-making-of-your-meal|publisher=BuzzFeed|date=2016-10-02|accessdate=2017-08-10|language=en|archive-date=2017-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730040018/https://www.buzzfeed.com/carolineodonovan/the-not-so-wholesome-reality-behind-the-making-of-your-meal|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年2月，藍圍裙宣布在紐澤西州的{{tsl|en|Linden, New Jersey|林登 (紐澤西州)|林登}}建立第四座履行中心。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Iati|first1=Maria|title=Blue Apron to bring 2K jobs to Linden facility|url=http://www.nj.com/union/index.ssf/2017/02/blue_apron_to_bring_2k_jobs_to_nj_build_linden_ful.html|accessdate=2017-05-10|publisher=NJ Advance Media|date=2017-02-08|language=en|archive-date=2017-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170529052905/http://www.nj.com/union/index.ssf/2017/02/blue_apron_to_bring_2k_jobs_to_nj_build_linden_ful.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年6月29日，藍圍裙透過[[紐約證券交易所|紐約證券交易所]][[首次公開發行|首次公開發行]]3000萬股A類[[普通股|普通股]]（[[股票代碼|股票代碼]]為APRN），成為美國首家[[股票上市|上市]]的快煮餐公司<ref>{{Cite news|title=Blue Apron’s Shares Flat in Trading Debut|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/blue-aprons-shares-edge-higher-in-trading-debut-1498747808|newspaper=[[Wall_Street_Journal|Wall Street Journal]]|date=2017-06-29|accessdate=2020-08-23|issn=0099-9660|language=en-US|author1=Corrie Driebusch|author2=Imani Moise|subscription=yes|archive-date=2018-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230164153/https://www.wsj.com/articles/blue-aprons-shares-edge-higher-in-trading-debut-1498747808|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但因[[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]收購[[全食超市|全食超市]]對交易市場造成影響<ref>{{Cite web|title=為什麼讓人們自行DIY餐點的Meal Kits，尚未掀起烹飪革命？|url=https://www.thenewslens.com/feature/timefortune/75562|accessdate=2020-08-23|date=2017-08-10|author=Alexandra Sifferlin|translator=許睿洋|work=The News Lens 關鍵評論網|publisher=[[時代_(雜誌)|TIME]]|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824072637/https://www.thenewslens.com/feature/timefortune/75562|dead-url=no}}</ref>，藍圍裙在融資過程中籌集到3億美元，比預期金額減少三分之一，每股定價自原先的15－17美元調低至10美元，其估值亦從最後一次融資時的22億降至18.9億美元。<ref name="Lauren Hirsch"/><ref>{{Cite web|title=半成品食材電商 Blue Apron上市|url=http://www.singtaousa.com/la/15-財經/179444-半成品食材電商Blue+Apron上市/|accessdate=2020-08-23|date=2017-07-01|work=[[星島日報|星島日報]]|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824072638/https://www.singtaousa.com/la/15-%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93/179444-%E5%8D%8A%E6%88%90%E5%93%81%E9%A3%9F%E6%9D%90%E9%9B%BB%E5%95%86Blue+Apron%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

自上市以來，[[華爾街|華爾街]]將藍圍裙的股價砍至一半，幾乎無法保全其[[獨角獸企業|獨角獸企業]]的地位，該公司於2017年10月宣布在發布下次[[財務報表|財務報表]]前進行人事重組，辦公室及履行中心將有6％的員工被裁員<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1701114/000110465917062779/a17-24139_28k.htm |title= Form 8K |publisher= [[美國證券交易委員會|美國證券交易委員會]] |date= 2017-10-18 |accessdate= 2020-08-23 |language= en |archive-date= 2019-11-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191106125230/https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1701114/000110465917062779/a17-24139_28k.htm |dead-url= no }}</ref>，預估約300名員工受到影響。<ref>{{cite news |url= https://techcrunch.com/2017/10/18/blue-apron-is-laying-off-6-of-its-staff/ |title= Blue Apron is laying off hundreds of employees |publisher= Tech Crunch |date= 2017-10-18 |first= Matthew |last= Lynley |accessdate= 2020-08-23 |language= en |archive-date= 2020-08-17 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200817195748/https://techcrunch.com/2017/10/18/blue-apron-is-laying-off-6-of-its-staff/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=今年IPO最慘代表！食譜配送新創Blue Apron裁員近300名員工|url=https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/46608/blue-apron-is-laying-off-6-of-its-staff|author=高敬原|accessdate=2020-08-23|date=2017-10-19|work=數位時代|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019190225/https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/46608/blue-apron-is-laying-off-6-of-its-staff|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年11月，藍圍裙因持續虧損，其股價已不及發行價的三分之一。<ref>{{Cite web|title=生鮮電商死亡潮？ Blue Apron燒錢用戶又不黏|url=https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171122/1057543.htm|accessdate=2020-08-23|author=|date=2017-11-22|format=|work=虎嗅網|publisher=ETtoday 新聞雲|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824072640/https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171122/1057543.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年11月30日，藍圍裙宣布布拉德·迪克森（Brad Dickerson）接替馬特·薩爾茲伯格出任[[首席執行長|首席執行長]]，而薩爾茲伯格則繼續擔任該公司董事長。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://techcrunch.com/2017/11/30/blue-apron-loses-its-ceo/|title=Blue Apron loses its CEO|last=Roof|first=Katie|work=TechCrunch|date=2017-12-01|accessdate=2020-08-23|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817195947/https://techcrunch.com/2017/11/30/blue-apron-loses-its-ceo/|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2018年3月26日，藍圍裙自首次公開募股以來，其[[市值|市值]]已蒸發81.4％。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Blue Apron Stock Hits New Low as Square Gets Huge Price-Target Hike - Schaeffer's Investment Research|url=https://www.schaeffersresearch.com/content/news/2018/03/26/blue-apron-stock-hits-new-low-as-square-gets-huge-price-target-hike|author=Josh Selway|date=2018-06-24|accessdate=2020-08-23|work=Schaeffers Investment Research|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727014609/https://www.schaeffersresearch.com/content/news/2018/03/26/blue-apron-stock-hits-new-low-as-square-gets-huge-price-target-hike|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年5月，藍圍裙開始在加州的17家[[好市多|好市多]]銷售4種快煮餐餐盒，代表著該公司已進入實體[[零售|零售]]領域<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/costco-sells-blue-apron-meal-kits-2018-5|title=Costco now sells Blue Apron — and the meal kits are 30% off|last=Peterson|first=Hayley|date=2018-03-05|work=Business Insider|access-date=2018-03-05|language=en|archive-date=2018-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180504044049/https://www.businessinsider.com/costco-sells-blue-apron-meal-kits-2018-5|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而原任職於{{tsl|en|Acosta Sales & Marketing|Acosta銷售與市場營銷公司}}的蒂姆·本斯利（Tim Bensley）則進入藍圍裙擔任[[首席財務長|首席財務長]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Blue Apron Appoints Tim Bensley as Chief Financial Officer|url=https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20180517005260/en/Blue-Apron-Appoints-Tim-Bensley-Chief-Financial|accessdate=2020-08-23|date=2018-05-17|work=[[Business_Wire|Business Wire]]|publisher=Blue Apron|location=New York|language=en|archive-date=2018-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180517145829/https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20180517005260/en/Blue-Apron-Appoints-Tim-Bensley-Chief-Financial|dead-url=no}}</ref>

