b/20191214044333/https://www.cnbc.com/2018/12/28/blue-apron-shares-bounce-back-to-over-1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Blue Apron Links With Dieters in Comeback Effort|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/blue-apron-links-with-dieters-in-comeback-effort-11545836401|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|date=2018-12-26|accessdate=2020-08-24|issn=0099-9660|language=en-US|first=Heather|last=Haddon|subscription=yes|archive-date=2019-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190928180702/https://www.wsj.com/articles/blue-apron-links-with-dieters-in-comeback-effort-11545836401|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年4月，琳達·科茲洛夫斯基（Linda Kozlowsk）接替布拉德·迪克森出任首席執行長，而迪克森則以顧問身分續留公司。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Blue Apron CEO and CTO are leaving the company|url=https://www.cnn.com/2019/04/02/business/blue-apron-ceo-resigns/index.html|date=2019-04-02|accessdate=2020-08-23|author=Danielle Wiener-Bronner|work=[[CNN|CNN]]|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820234835/https://www.cnn.com/2019/04/02/business/blue-apron-ceo-resigns/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Blue Apron CEO Brad Dickerson to step down|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-blue-apron-hldg-ceo-brad-dickerson-idUSKCN1RE2H4|author=Soundarya J|location=Bengaluru|editor=James Emmanuel|newspaper=Reuters|date=2019-04-02|accessdate=2020-08-24|language=en|archive-date=2020-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331113132/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-blue-apron-hldg-ceo-brad-dickerson-idUSKCN1RE2H4|dead-url=no}}</ref>

